29 (3) The Chancellor of the University of Maine System or the chancellor's designee;
30 and
31 (4) The President of the Maine Community College System or the president's
32 designee.
33 C. The members of the board who are not ex officio members are appointed by the
34 Governor and subject to confirmation by the Senate and must be individuals or
