37 economy sector as specified in the bylaws of the center. When making appointments
38 under this paragraph, the Governor shall consider the unique multidisciplinary nature
39 of the State's blue economy sector and shall consult with the Board of Directors of the
40 Maine Technology Institute and the board of directors of the Finance Authority of
41 Maine to ensure the alignment of those appointments with the State's economic
42 development strategies. Membership under this paragraph must include:
